race.comment: OFFA'S DYKE (6) couldn't quite deliver for supporters last time but looks to be hitting his straps now fourth-up. Milnes sticks from a good draw and she can get it done this time. GRINZINGER GOLD (8) was well fancied throughout her last campaign without breaking through. Has been prepared with three trials and should be forward from the low draw. Can make a bright return. STARS ARE ALIGNING (12) showed good tactical speed here fresh and fought hard to just miss. Sure to have come on from that and can give another bold sight. ARLO'S DREAM (1) improved sharply here last time when beaten narrowly. Has further improvement to come and is in the mix.
